and-new-4bd69b82.html?songid=2bd608a6">卢卡</a>”，“<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/stats/songs/brand-new-4bd69b82.html?songid=4bd427f2">在底部</a>”，然后他们将两首歌他们的现场首演。这些都是“浪费”和“打击”，它们都出现在他们的最新专辑《 2017年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brand-new-release-first-album-since-2009-science-fiction-2125859">科幻小说</a>》中。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlist/brand-new/2025/the-bomb-factory-dallas-tx-135b0129.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>setList.fm</em></a>的说法，该节目以其2006年的歌曲“耶稣基督”和“营”和“无法拿出”的演绎结束，尽管当天早些时候在Soundcheck上演奏，但两者都没有成为最后的CIT。</p><p>查看更多录像和下面的完整列表。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="全新现场 - 击球手（现场首次亮相） - 炸弹工厂，德克萨斯州达拉斯-3/26/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vhV1VErjwS8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="全新现场 - 废物（现场处女作） - 炸弹厂，德克萨斯州达拉斯-3/26/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bGodbPpbkfU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="全新现场 - 播种季节 - 德克萨斯州达拉斯的炸弹工厂-3/26/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UGnDKk7qKYE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="全新现场直播 - 没人知道的安静事物 - 炸弹厂，达拉斯，德克萨斯州-3/26/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0-nzRzzuBmw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; 