nye-alice-merton@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kanye-alice-merton@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kanye-alice-merton@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kanye-alice-merton@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/kanye-alice-merton@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a>面临德国歌手兼作词人爱丽丝·默顿（Alice Merton）的诉讼，其中一首歌中的一首歌未经许可在他的“秃鹰2”专辑中出现。</p><p>这位歌手兼作曲家因其2017年的热门歌曲“ No Roots”而获得最佳认可，据报道，在星期二（3月25日）在加利福尼亚州（3月25日），对说唱歌手提起了新的诉讼。</p><p>在诉讼中，她声称Ye未经许可就她的2022年歌曲“ Blindside”取样。据称在他的歌曲中使用的样本使用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-cudi">Kid Cudi</a> ，名为“ Gun To My Heard”，该样本出现在他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-sign">Ty Dolla $ ign</a>的合作专辑中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-release-vultures-2-deluxe-with-new-track-3781830">“ Vultures 2”</a> 。</p><p>在说唱歌手在2023年12月的一次听力聚会上预览曲目之后，默顿首先意识到了样本的使用。她声称他没有事先要求许可，并且仅在2024年2月才征求清算。</p><p>当时，默顿的出版商BMG未允许，后来解释说，由于West的“价值观违反了我们的价值观”（通过<a href="https://www.stereogum.com/2301873/alice-merton-sues-kanye-west-over-sample-she-denied-because-of-his-antisemitism/news/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Stereogum</em></a> ），因此拒绝了样本的使用。他们还提请注意以下事实：默顿是大屠杀幸存者的后代，并且“不愿妥协她的个人信仰，并希望不与西部的联系”，因为他一再分享了他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">认为自己是纳粹分子</a>。</p><p>虽然这首歌没有在“ Vultures 2”的最初曲目列表中出现，但它确实出现在专辑的Digital <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-release-vultures-2-deluxe-with-new-track-3781830">Deluxe Edition</a>上。 </p><figure id="attachment_3840483" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840483" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840483" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West.-CREDIT_-Stephane-Cardinale-Corbis_Corbis-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3840483" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特。图片来源：Stephane Cardinale  -  Corbis/Corbis通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在文件中的其他地方，默顿声称这首歌从专辑中省略了，导致她受到了Ye粉丝的威胁，并指控West的团队无视BMG的停止和停止信。</p><p>这不是韦斯特第一次在他的“秃鹰”专辑中未经授权的样品中发现自己在热水中。去年，他引起了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑安息日</a>主唱奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）的反对，他上了社交媒体<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">，呼吁说唱歌手未经许可就他的一首歌进行采样</a>。</p><p>在得知韦斯特（West）将黑人安息日歌曲“钢铁侠”（Iron Man）的样本循环成他的一首歌之后，金属偶像在冗长的帖子中击中了他，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">称说唱歌手为“反犹太派”</a> 。</p><p>沙龙·奥斯本（Sharon Osbourne） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-says-kanye-west-fucked-with-the-wrong-jew-this-time-3585447">随后在韦斯特（West）猛烈抨击，说他“这次与错误的犹太人搞砸了”</a> ，在派往西部的停止和停止后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-removes-sample-of-black-sabbaths-iron-man-after-ozzy-osbourne-criticism-3585627">说唱歌手删除了样本 - 用模糊的吉他反馈代替了样本</a>。</p><p>除此之外，去年2月，唐娜·萨默（Donna Summer）的丈夫布鲁斯·苏达诺（Bruce Sudano）对西部和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-ign">泰恩·$ ign</a>提起了版权侵权诉讼， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donna-summers-estate-sues-kanye-west-and-ty-dolla-ign-for-illegal-use-of-i-feel-love-3594065">声称这两个说唱歌手无权在他们的专辑中取样1977年的迪斯科舞厅“我的感觉爱”</a> 。</p><p>歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-ty-dolla-igns-vultures-song-removed-from-spotify-after-complaint-by-donna-summers-estate-3587972">“ Good（Do not Die）”中出现的示例，并发出文件后，该歌曲已从Spotify和其他流媒体服务中删除</a>。随后分享的是， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-and-donna-summers-estate-reach-settlement-over-use-of-i-feel-love-3768363">西部和萨默的遗产终于对6月的“非法”使用达成和解。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3837750" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837750" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837750" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）参加第67届格莱美奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Kanye-West22000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837750" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）参加了第67届格莱美奖。图片来源：弗雷泽·哈里森/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在其他坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的新闻中，这位说唱歌手最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-deletes-offensive-tweet-about-beyonce-and-jay-zs-children-3847519">在分享了一系列有关碧昂斯（Beyoncé）和杰伊（Jay-Z）的孩子的进攻帖子</a>后引发了广泛的批评。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-drops-new-album-bully-as-short-film-3847412">还将他的新专辑“ Bully”作为一部短片</a>，并在X/Twitter上<a href="https://twitter.com/kanyewest/status/1901014464637685988">发行了新歌</a>“ Lonely Roads To To Sunshine”。</p><p>在后者的帖子中，这位说唱歌手声称它以耻辱的说唱大<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/diddy">亨迪迪</a>（Mogul Diddy）以及韦斯特（West）的11岁女儿North为特色。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kim-kardashian-and-kanye-west-at-war-after-he-drops-song-seemingly-featuring-diddy-and-their-daughter-north-3846591">这首歌引发了坎耶和他的前妻金·卡戴珊（Kim Kardashian）之间的“战争”，她与她分享了北方</a>。</p><p>在此之前，他放弃了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">一系列引起争议的帖子</a>，使他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">对犹太社区的道歉撤销了他过去的反犹太言论</a>，然后继续宣布自己为“纳粹”。</p><p>最近，他取笑了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sunday-service-choir-jesus-is-born-review-2591297">周日服务合唱团活动</a>的回归，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-teases-sunday-service-return-then-posts-photo-of-kkk-robe-3844826">在社交媒体上张贴了KKK长袍的照片</a>。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-sued-by-alice-merton-over-unauthorised-sample-in-vultures-2-3849720">Kanye West sued by Alice Merton over unauthorised sample in &#39;Vultures 2&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
